      <p>Currently, DBM houses 73 Deaf children in its school, while over 200 Deaf church members receive spiritual and community support. With the capacity to welcome more students, DBM faces financial challenges in meeting daily expenses. To sustain this mission, each child requires $25 per month, an amount that covers food, education, and healthcare.</p>
